    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy, always garage-kept and meticulously cared for. You won't find a single blemish on it. If you're looking for total perfection, this is definitely the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
