    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive wide-body icon. This example features the M96/03 3.6L flat-six, meticulously maintained with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides precise engagement, delivering power through the viscous-coupling AWD system. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory Turbo-spec suspension with four-piston Monoblock 'Big Red' calipers and cross-drilled rotors. Zero signs of bore scoring; oil analysis is consistent and clean. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the discerning enthusiast who values mechanical transparency and structural rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
