      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and fragrant, with the carpets protected by original floor mats since day one. Every button, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it comes with a comprehensive binder of every service performed at the authorized dealership, including a recent major interval service and fresh performance tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. No accidents, no modifications, smoke-free, and a clean title in hand.",
